last_episode_to_air.name: Dogcathalon
last_episode_to_air.overview: Tag must make sure Pawston looks ready to host the Dogcathalon. Crew captain Tag coaches her loved ones through the Sky, Boat and Speedway races.

name: Go, Dog. Go!
overview: Handy and inventive pup Tag chases adventure with her best pal, Scooch, solving problems and helping the citizens of Pawston along the way.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Adventurous pups Tag and Scooch are going everywhere this season, from exciting places all around Pawston to the bright lights of Chew York City!

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: The gang's on-the-go adventures take an un-fur-gettable turn when Tag, Scooch and friends welcome a new family to Pawston and show them all around town!

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Tag and her best friend Scooch love lending a paw to their friends around Pawston, whether it's delivering cookie boxes or hosting the Dogcathalon!

episodes.name: Welcome to Pawston
episodes.overview: Tag and her new friend, Scooch, make their way across town to attend a party in a tree.

episodes.name: Ruff Day on the Job
episodes.overview: Mail dog Gerald is being chased and can't make his deliveries!

episodes.name: Dark Park Bark Lark
episodes.overview: Tag helps Scooch do his chores so they can go to the Barkapellas' concert.

episodes.name: The Fast and the Curious
episodes.overview: With dreams of becoming a Race Cadet, Tag asks Scooch to be her crew chief.

episodes.name: Old Dog, New Tricks
episodes.overview: Tag and Grandpaw team up to compete in the Barker Family Talent Show.

episodes.name: Snoozie-Hullabaloozi
episodes.overview: It's a special day for sleeping and snoozing in Pawston... but Tag's not tired!

episodes.name: Show Dog, Show
episodes.overview: Cheddar Biscuit can't stop picking up clowns on the way to Tag's car show.

episodes.name: Keys to Victory
episodes.overview: The not-yet Race Cadets face a second challenge: finding Sam Whippet's keys.

episodes.name: Pupcakes
episodes.overview: Scooch's pupcakes are amazing, and Tag is determined to sell them.

episodes.name: Stink or Swim
episodes.overview: Scooch and Tag try to clean up the beach, but Frank and Beans keep making it messier!

episodes.name: A Ball for All
episodes.overview: Dogs in Pawston give balls to each other on Ballentine's Day to show how much they care. But Tag and Scooch aren't prepared and need to find balls fast!

episodes.name: Ding Dong Day
episodes.overview: Paw brings Tag to the doorbell store for Take Your Kid to Work Day.

episodes.name: Grand Sam
episodes.overview: The third Race Cadet challenge is an obstacle course that takes teamwork to win.

episodes.name: Clucky Day
episodes.overview: Scooch is sad he's missing out on a special day, so Tag plans a big surprise.

episodes.name: Take Me Out to the Fetch Game
episodes.overview: The Pawston Get Sox are supposed to play ball... but where are the players?

episodes.name: Dog the Right Thing
episodes.overview: For the final Race Cadet challenge, the three teams must find scattered car parts, put them together at Pawston Pawtomotive and race to the finish!

episodes.name: Snow Dog Snow
episodes.overview: Sniffsmas in in the air! But when Sandra Paws crashes her sleigh, it's up to Tag and Scooch ― and a selfless act of kindness ― to save the holiday.

episodes.name: All Paws on Deck
episodes.overview: A thoughtful Tag tries to re-create the first time her parents met.

episodes.name: Bonestand and Deliver
episodes.overview: Tag rallies a crew to rebuild the Bonestand for Pawston's 100-year anniversary.

episodes.name: Catch Me If You Sam
episodes.overview: On Tag's first day as a Race Cadet, she breaks the rules to win ― then learns a big lesson.

episodes.name: Toy Driver
episodes.overview: Ma donates Tag's old toys to puppies in need.

episodes.name: Frank and Beans with Chili
episodes.overview: Beans feels left out when his stunt-dog cousin, Chili, comes to town and Frank seems to spend all of his time with him.

episodes.name: Little Hound on the Prairie
episodes.overview: Tag learns about her ancestors.

episodes.name: Chaser and Chewer
episodes.overview: Tag and Scooch play heroes while waiting for the next issue of their favorite comic book.

episodes.name: Recipe for Adventure
episodes.overview: Grandmaw and Tag gather ingredients for a famous family recipe.

episodes.name: Raiders of the Lost Bark
episodes.overview: Scooch and Tag go on a treasure hunt to find an ancient golden slipper.

episodes.name: Slow Dog Slow
episodes.overview: The Race Cadets pair up with senior dogs for a relaxing day that's anything but!

episodes.name: Board Silly
episodes.overview: Tag and friends turn the streets of Pawston into an interactive board game.

episodes.name: Sing for the Fences
episodes.overview: The dogs compete to write a new anthem for the town's anniversary bash.

episodes.name: Fast Frank's Fixit
episodes.overview: The Pawtomotive Garage gets some competition when a new shop opens up nearby.

episodes.name: Tail-kwondo
episodes.overview: The mysterious Master Wag invites Scooch to train at his secret cave.

episodes.name: Happy Birthday Pawston
episodes.overview: It's the day of Pawston's big party, but Tag still doesn't know if pop star Kelly Korgi is coming to perform. Can the pups fetch an answer in time?

episodes.overview: Sam Whippet needs to fill every seat in the Speedway so he can win his rematch.

episodes.overview: Sam Whippet challenges the race cadets to deliver his cookie boxes as fast as they can.

episodes.overview: Muttfield the Magnificent disappears before Yip's birthday party.

episodes.name: Tail to the Chief
episodes.overview: Tag takes over running Pawston so Mayor Sniffington can take a day off.

episodes.name: Chaser and Chewer: Part Chew
episodes.overview: Flea and Thunder kidnap Scooch's stuffed chicken, Cluckles!

episodes.name: The Puppy Whisperer
episodes.overview: When Beans offers to babysit Yip, Tag has a hard time getting her baby brother back.

episodes.name: Doggy Book of World Records
episodes.overview: Tag and Scooch try to get into the "Doggy Book of World Records."

episodes.name: The Pawmazing Race
episodes.overview: Tag enters the Barkers to compete on their favorite TV game show, "The Pawmazing Race." She wants to win, but her family just wants to have fun.

episodes.overview: Tag must figure out a way across the river so her cat friends can celebrate Yarn Ball Day.

episodes.name: No Part Harmony
episodes.overview: The Barkapellas won't perform their concert without new ties.

episodes.name: Happy Pawtomotiversary
episodes.overview: Tag surprises her grandparents by recreating an old photo of their garage.

episodes.name: Winner, Winner, Lasagna Dinner
episodes.overview: Wind and Tag compete in lasagna challenges to become Sam's new crew chief.

episodes.overview: Tag makes a movie to help Pawston win the chance to host the Dogcathalon.

episodes.name: Stay, Dog. Stay!
episodes.overview: Frank and Beans stay at the Barkers' house while Tag repairs their roof.

episodes.name: Whatever It Cakes
episodes.overview: Scooch needs help transporting a cake to Chew York City for his favorite cooking show.

episodes.name: Haturday
episodes.overview: Tag searches all over town for Lady Lydia's missing hat feathers.

episodes.name: Trick or Thief
episodes.overview: On Howl-oween, Tag investigates the case of the missing pup-clairs.

episodes.name: Meow-Lo-Ween
episodes.overview: Tag assembles a team of Howl-oween experts to put on a parade in Meowbuquerque.

episodes.name: The Trouble with Kibbles
episodes.overview: Maw recounts the day she saved the entire city of Pawston by flying a blimp.

episodes.name: Road to Kindness
episodes.overview: Frank enrolls in a kindness class so he can attend Roller Disco Night.

episodes.name: How Tag Got Her Tag
episodes.overview: The Barkers recount the story of how Tag got her race flag tag as a puppy.

episodes.name: Blankie Blaster
episodes.overview: Tag promises Spike she'll deliver his blankie before his space mission.

episodes.name: Chaser and Chewer: Part Flea
episodes.overview: Flea plans to do "bad guy" stuff all over town, but not if Chaser, Chewer — and Thunder — can stop him.

episodes.name: Sing for Your Pupper
episodes.overview: Wagnes auditions for Pupsy Cline's world tour.
